snippet.title: Hot Wheels™ Rift Rally — Smart RC Car + Video Game
snippet.description:
Drift, stunt and race on a mixed reality track that YOU create with Hot Wheels™ Rift Rally! 

https://www.riftrally.com 

Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/velanstudios
Subscribe to our YouTube channel: https://www.youtube.com/velanstudios8518

PlayStation and Apple device sold separately. Free software download required.
